OL,5,BMY WISH FOR 1998Gby Una, St Anne's,    
OL,6,GFinaghy, Belfast                       
OL,7,CMy wish for 1998 is that I could get a 
OL,8,Ckitten. It would be marvellous to have 
OL,9,Cone because they are so cute. They are 
OL,10,Calso very fluffy and soft.             
OL,12,CMy friend has a kitten. It is grey and 
OL,13,Cwhite - it is double cute.             
OL,15,CHer baby brother David lifts him up by 
OL,16,Cthe tail. Then the kitten runs away and
OL,17,Chides. If I am there I go over and pet 
OL,18,Chim very gently.                       
